</comment>
                            <comment id="14250710" author="romseygeek" created="Wed, 17 Dec 2014 22:35:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Just bumped into this trying to cut over a bunch of test cases to core discovery for &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-6840&quot; title=&quot;Remove legacy solr.xml mode&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-6840&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-6840&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.  Here&apos;s a nice simple patch to fix it.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
